description: Bulkogi is a Korean BBQ and Korean/Mex fusion truck with high quality food at street level prices, with a little bit of Korea in every bite!We operate in the Raleigh/Durham area :) Our menu consists of many fusion items( like our tasty tacos, flavorful burritos, almost famous steak n' cheese, popular Kimchi Buldogs, unique Kimchi quesadillas, and more!) All of the items on the menu were conocted by the owner of Bulkogi! We are also known for our yummy Korean BBQ! Come check us out, you won't regret it !!!
name: Bulkogi Korean BBQ
